#: ../../effects_and_compositions/video_effects/generate/drawgrid.rst:1
msgid ""
"KDE, Kdenlive, video editor, help, learn, easy, effects, filter, video "
"effects, generate, draw grid"
msgstr ""
"KDE, Kdenlive, videobewerker, hulp, leren, gemakkelijk, effecten, filter, "
"video-effecten, genereren, raster tekenen"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/video_effects/generate/drawgrid.rst:16
msgid "Draw Grid"
msgstr "Raster tekenen"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/video_effects/generate/drawgrid.rst:18
msgid "This effect/filter draws a colored grid on the input video."
msgstr "Dit effect/filter tekent een gekleurd raster op de originele video."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/video_effects/generate/drawgrid.rst:20
msgid "The effect has keyframes."
msgstr "Dit effect heeft keyframes."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/video_effects/generate/drawgrid.rst:28
msgid "Draw Grid effect"
msgstr "Raster tekenen effect"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/video_effects/generate/drawgrid.rst:30
msgid ""
"**X / Y Offset** - Defines the starting point of the grid in pixels from the "
"top left-hand corner of the monitor (coordinates are based on the project "
"dimension settings)"
msgstr ""
"**X / Y Offset** - Definieert het startpunt van het raster in pixels vanuit "
"de hoek linksboven van de monitor (coördinaten zijn gebaseerd op de "
"projectinstellingen voor de afmetingen)"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/video_effects/generate/drawgrid.rst:32
msgid "**Width** - Defines the distance between vertical grid lines in pixels"
msgstr ""
"**Breedte** - definieert de afstand tussen de verticale rasterlijnen in "
"pixels"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/video_effects/generate/drawgrid.rst:34
msgid ""
"**Height** - Defines the distance between horizontal grid lines in pixels"
msgstr ""
"**Hoogte** - definieert de afstand tussen de horizontale rasterlijnen in "
"pixels"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/video_effects/generate/drawgrid.rst:36
msgid "**Thickness** - Defines the thickness of the lines in pixels"
msgstr "**Dikte** - definieert de dikte van de lijnen in pixels"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/video_effects/generate/drawgrid.rst:38
msgid "**Color** - Defines the color for the grid"
msgstr "**Kleur** - definieert de kleur van het raster"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/video_effects/generate/drawgrid.rst:43
msgid ""
"As of this writing and in version 23.04.2 the color parameter is being "
"ignored and black is used."
msgstr ""
"Op het moment dat dit wordt geschreven en in versie 23.04.2 wordt de kleur-"
"parameter genegeerd en wordt zwart gebruikt."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/video_effects/generate/drawgrid.rst:45
msgid ""
"This effect can be used in combination with the :ref:`effects-"
"chroma_key_basic` or :ref:`effects-chroma_key_advanced` effects to create "
"interesting transitions by animating the number of grid lines and their "
"thickness."
msgstr ""
"Dit effect kan in combinatie met de :ref:`effects-chroma_key_basic` of de :"
"ref:`effects-chroma_key_advanced` effecten worden gebruikt om interessante "
"overgangen te creëren door het aantal rasterlijnen en hun dikte te laten "
"variëren."
